      <title>搜狗输入法实现自定义短语快捷输入front-matter</title>
      <link href="/2018/03/22/%E6%90%9C%E7%8B%97%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9F%AD%E8%AF%AD/"/>
      <url>/2018/03/22/%E6%90%9C%E7%8B%97%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9F%AD%E8%AF%AD/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>搜狗输入法如何使用自定义短语实现Hexo 搭建网页过程中的front-matter 的快捷化输入</p><h2 id="front-matter-的格式如下："><a href="#front-matter-的格式如下：" class="headerlink" title="front matter 的格式如下："></a>front matter 的格式如下：</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: group</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018.03.21 15:54</span><br><span class="line">layout: links</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="百度输入法是如何实现的"><a href="#百度输入法是如何实现的" class="headerlink" title="百度输入法是如何实现的"></a>百度输入法是如何实现的</h3><p>在外网看到了百度输入法通过构建自定义短语实现了对于front matter 快捷化的输入，自定义短语如下：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ 1,ifm=#&#123;Hexo front-matter&#125;#---</span><br><span class="line">$ \title:</span><br><span class="line">$ \id: $(month_mm)$(day_dd)$(fullhour)$(minute)$(second)</span><br><span class="line">$ \date: $(year)-$(month_mm)-$(day_dd) $(fullhour):$(minute):$(second)</span><br><span class="line">$ \updated: $(year)-$(month_mm)-$(day_dd) $(fullhour):$(minute):$(second)</span><br><span class="line">$ \categories:</span><br><span class="line">$ \tags:</span><br><span class="line">$ \permalink: https://likianta.coding.me/2018/category/$(month_mm)$(day_dd)$(fullhour)$(minute)$(second)/</span><br><span class="line">$ \---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>通过使用上面的自定义短语实现了对于日期时间以及内容的动态化快捷录入，那么直接复制到搜狗输入法里面是不可以的，两者对于自定义短语的使用有着一定的不同，因此，搜狗输入法如何能够进行快捷的对于front matter 的录入呢？</p><h3 id="搜狗输入法中是如何实现的"><a href="#搜狗输入法中是如何实现的" class="headerlink" title="搜狗输入法中是如何实现的"></a>搜狗输入法中是如何实现的</h3><p>右键属性设置-&gt;高级-&gt;自定义短语设置-&gt;直接编辑配置文件-&gt;最后一行添加以下自定义配置：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ifm,1=</span><br><span class="line">$ #---</span><br><span class="line">$ title:</span><br><span class="line">$ date: $year.$month_mm.$day_dd $fullhour:$minute</span><br><span class="line">$ tags:</span><br><span class="line">$ -</span><br><span class="line">$ categories:</span><br><span class="line">$ thumbnail:</span><br><span class="line">$ ---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上</p>]]></content>
      
